            </div>
			<div style="clear:both"></div>	
			<div class="post" id="post-6048">
				<div class="entry">
					<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/OpenMoons.jpg"><img title="OpenMoons" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/10/OpenMoons.jpg" alt="" width="467" height="68" /></a><span style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.25pt; text-align: right; font-weight: normal;">.</span></h2>
<h1 style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">! אקואים יקרים </span></h1>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">.תחרות הירחים הסתיימה ורציתי להודות לכם באופן אישי על ההשקעה והשיתוף</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">היה מרגש לראות כמה מוכשרים אתם בעיצוב, פשוט יש לכם את זה, בהחלט זו אחת</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">!!התחרויות שתיזכר</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">ראינו כמה יפים הבתים שלכם, כמה מושקעות החוות החקלאיות שלכם</span><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: #222222;" lang="HE"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">!ואיזה מארחים מופלאים אתם, אני גאה בכולכם! כל הכבוד</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"><span style="font-family: Wingdings;"> </span>היה ממש ממש קשה לבחור את הזוכים בתחרויות העיצוב עד שהחלטתי לשבור את </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"><span style="font-family: Wingdings;">J </span>החוקים ולהכפיל את כמות הזוכים </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">!שוב כל הכבוד לכולכם על ההשתתפות</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">אורטלית</span><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: #222222;" lang="HE"> </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: right; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: right; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; color: #222222;" lang="HE">. </span></p>
<h2 style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: red;" lang="HE">:ובלי עוד תוספות, הנה רשימת הזוכים בתחרות עיצוב הבית</span></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: right; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">. </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><strong><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">:במקום הראשון</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"> </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">שרקי &#8211; </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;">Sharky</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"> </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">אוסקר &#8211; </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;">razbd5660</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"><strong>:במקום השני</strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"> </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">מסעדה -</span> <span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;"> talya3335 </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">בית הספורט של עידן -</span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;"> edan2000 </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"><strong>:במקום השלישי</strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"> </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">בוטנאי &#8211; </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;">galinalove18</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-align: center; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 7.0pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE"> </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;" lang="HE">הכיתה שלי &#8211; </span><span style="font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: &amp;amp;amp; mso-fareast-font-family: &amp;amp;amp; color: #1f497d;">mali2442</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; text-align: right; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">.</p>
